Class Person

  • java.lang.Object
    • Person
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Employee

    public class Person
extends java.lang.Object
    Person is a base class containing attributes typically belonging to a person. It is the superclass of the Employee class.
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Nathan Kiernan 15088410
